reviewText: Love the album and the artists voice

What a beautiful video about Sam Smith! I loved every minute of it. I have seen quite a few Sam Smith documentaries but this one is by far, the best one! If you're a huge Sam Smith fan, this video is for you! You won't be disappointed one bit!
Not what i thought it was going to be.  Thought it was all music not an interview DVD.
NO music. It is just a bunch of random interviews.  A total waste of money.  Do not buy this.  I didn't bother to return it.  I THREW IT IN THE TRASH!
